How to use:
* Copy then paste the path of the first directory.
* Then copy then paste the path of the second dyrectory.
* Click enter and will see the size of first directory then the second.

* The purpose of the project is training asynchronous programing in java and working with File class.

* Examples:
C:\Users\Laptop\Downloads\08. Java-Advanced-Files-and-Streams-Lab-Resources
C:\Users\Laptop\Documents\NumbersFrom1To50-project
